    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/0e92e6cd739235e865cafd0160f83322.poster.avif?t=1763356630\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/0e92e6cd739235e865cafd0160f83322.webm?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/0e92e6cd739235e865cafd0160f83322.mp4?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗科幻 × 东方王朝</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上旅程，探索一个融合了东方神秘主义与黑暗科幻的古老世界。你的任务是刺杀安南之王——他通过邪恶的手段获得了永生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冥界诸神对国王逆天改命的行为震怒，因而选中一名被遗忘的亡魂，让其重返人间，只为执行唯一的使命：杀死那个欺骗死亡的王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/8bd4fd929d879a6ff8348b60bbaea406.poster.avif?t=1763356630\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/8bd4fd929d879a6ff8348b60bbaea406.webm?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/8bd4fd929d879a6ff8348b60bbaea406.mp4?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多形态亡魂</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为亡魂，你能够在生者与死者的领域之间切换不同的肉身形态。每一种形态都拥有独特的武器、技能树与能力。你还可以解锁多样的天赋，以匹配不同的战斗风格。寻找最契合的天赋组合，打造属于你的终极亡魂形态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当你死去，都可能以不同形态复活。但请注意——形态是有限资源。 一旦全部耗尽，你将被永远放逐回冥界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/084801ca1d2a7bdd6941808187a04157.poster.avif?t=1763356630\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/084801ca1d2a7bdd6941808187a04157.webm?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/084801ca1d2a7bdd6941808187a04157.mp4?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>残酷的格挡战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入激烈的战斗，利用连续的格挡反击、精准的闪避，以及原创的阴阳连击系统来击败敌人。收集多种独特武器，每种武器都拥有能扭转战局的强大能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路战斗至皇宫深处，对抗忠于国王的强大敌将。这些终极战将真正考验你的操作技巧、时机把握与战术思维。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/e289018e97cb189105193ca33296d395.poster.avif?t=1763356630\" width=608 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/e289018e97cb189105193ca33296d395.webm?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304010/extras/e289018e97cb189105193ca33296d395.mp4?t=1763356630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满谜团的安南旧都——这里区域相互交织，暗藏秘密通道与致命的精英敌人。在旅途中，你将收集武器、古老技能卷轴、稀有材料与强力强化道具，不断让你的亡魂更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逐步揭开国王永生的秘密，并决定旧王国的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会顺从冥界诸神的旨意，还是选择掌握自己的命运？</p>",
